| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4941 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 51a33ced-46ec-5573-b0b1-641b87cd5f70"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
